@startuml
[*] --> Idle

state Idle
Idle : entry / Display Welcome

Idle --> InsertedCard : Card Inserted / Get PIN

state InsertedCard
InsertedCard --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

state WaitingForPIN
WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN

state ValidatingPIN
ValidatingPIN --> MainMenu : Valid PIN / Display Menu
ValidatingPIN --> NotVerified : Invalid PIN / Prompt Again

state MainMenu
MainMenu --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Withdrawal Selected /\nRequest Withdrawal, Display Wait

state ProcessingWithdrawal
ProcessingWithdrawal --> DispensingCash : Withdrawal Approved /\nDispense Cash, Update Status

state DispensingCash
DispensingCash --> PrintingReceipt : Cash Dispensed /\nPrint Receipt,\nDisplay Cash Dispensed,\nConfirm Cash Dispensed

state PrintingReceipt
PrintingReceipt --> EjectingCard : Receipt Printed / Eject

state EjectingCard
EjectingCard --> Resetting : Card Ejected / Display Ejected

state Resetting
Resetting --> Idle : After (Elapsed Time)\n[Ready for Next User]

state NotVerified
NotVerified --> WaitingForPIN : PIN Re-Entered / Get PIN Again

Idle --> [*]
@enduml
